Has been over every night during the last week.
20/5/18 Several trainloads of American troops passing through going towards Lumbres.
22/5/18 Wrote home to Uncle Fred
27/5/18 After lunch walked over the hill to Bilques.
29/5/18 Wrote to Base Post Office.
